OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cwife's grandmother
OL,6,FA 39-year-old man has been jailed for
OL,7,Flife, serving a minimum of 24 years,
OL,8,Ffor the murder of his wife's 78-year-
OL,9,Fold grandmother.
OL,11,FJune Henty was getting ready to go
OL,12,FChristmas shopping with her daughter
OL,13,Fwhen Adam Wright, of Bishop's Waltham,
OL,14,Fvisited and demanded money.
OL,16,FWhen he was refused, Wright attacked
OL,17,Fher out of anger, and stabbed her more
OL,18,Fthan 100 times to the head, face and
OL,19,Fneck.
