OL,6,FJune Henty was later found by family
OL,7,Fmembers and taken to hospital, where
OL,8,Fshe underwent major surgery and spent
OL,9,F90 days in intensive care. She died on
OL,10,FJune 14, 2024.
OL,12,FShe identified Adam Wright as her
OL,13,Fattacker at the scene to family
OL,14,Fmembers and to emergency responders,
OL,15,Fand he was arrested that same day.
OL,17,FDesmond Duffy, of the Crown
OL,18,FProsecution Service, said: "This was a
OL,19,Ftruly horrific and senseless act of
OL,20,Fviolence against a much-loved family
OL,21,Fmember.
