OL,6,F"The sheer brutality is beyond
OL,7,Fcomprehension, and Wright's alcohol
OL,8,Fand drug consumption the previous
OL,9,Fnight offers no justification for the
OL,10,Flevel of anger and violence inflicted
OL,11,Fupon a woman.
OL,13,F"I hope as Wright faces the full
OL,14,Fconsequences of his actions, Mrs
OL,15,FHenty's loved ones can feel some sense
OL,16,Fof justice."
OL,18,FJune Henty's family said in a
OL,19,Fstatement: "Our beautiful mum June was
OL,20,Fbrutally taken away from us and as a
OL,21,Ffamily we are heartbroken.
